Set Shell "zsh"
Set Width 1200
Set Height 400
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set FontSize 16
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 40ms

Output whoami6.gif

Hide
Type "export PS1='darren@ForgeSworn.dev:bray $ '"
Enter
Sleep 0.3s
Type "cd /Users/darren/WebstormProjects/bray/site/demos"
Enter
Sleep 0.3s
Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 0.3s
Show

Type "./bray-demo.sh 'Use the whoami tool to check which identity is active'"
Enter
Sleep 15s
